column2: Chicken in Sauce - low protein & low phosphorus
column7: Please note that Dave’s Chicken in Sauce - low protein & and low phosphorus product mimics Hill’s k/d renal diet which is one that I would never feed to any cat in my care - including patients with kidney disease.  It was a very sad day when protein became the enemy of the feline kidney.  Please do not feed diets that are this low (or lower) in protein.
